      "style": "Normal",
      "source_kind": "paragraph",
      "page": 0,
      "region": "body"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b00011",
      "text": "2、报价方向:同时报出支付固定利率(bid)和收取固定利率(offer)两个方向。",
      "style": "Normal",
      "source_kind": "paragraph",
