      "region": "body"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b00012",
      "text": "3、报价时间窗口:每个交易日上午11:30至12:00,下午16:00至16:30。",
      "style": "Normal",
      "source_kind": "paragraph",
      "page": 0,
      "region": "body"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b00013",
      "text": "4、报价界面:中国外汇交易中心本币交易系统利率互换双向报价界面。",
      "style": "Normal",
      "source_kind": "paragraph",
